These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: crime, action, documentary, musical, sports, time-travel, drama
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: disco, metal, trance, d&b, electronic, hip-hop, pop
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: sailing, lacrosse, skiing, cricket, weightlifting, cycling, skateboarding
 1. the person watching sports movies is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
 3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the fan of metal and the fan of disco##2
 4. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 5. the fan of metal is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
 6. the person watching crime movies is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 7. the fan of d&b is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person watching sports movies##2
 8. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 9. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
10. the person watching drama movies is the fan of trance##1
11. the fan of hip-hop is the person watching musical movies##1
12. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
13. the person who's sport is sailing is the fan of electronic##1
14. the person watching time-travel movies is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person who's sport is skateboarding##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |    7     |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | crime     | time-travel | action | musical | drama  | documentary  |
| Music-Genre   | disco  | d&b        | metal  | pop     | hip-hop   | trance       | electronic   |
| Sport         | lacrosse   | skateboarding | cricket    | skiing  | weightlifting | cycling | sailing |

