.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-2::.
There are 7 different nationalities: brazilian, nigerian, turkish, spanish, malaysian, italian, american
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: golf, rowing, swimming, baseball, cycling, tennis, rugby
The people use 7 different means of transport: taxi, airplane, motorbike, subway, van, snowmobile, jet-ski
 1. the nigerian is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
 2. the person who's sport is cycling is the person who's sport is cycling##1
 3. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
 5. the person who's sport is golf is the american##1
 6. the brazilian is the person driving the subway##1
 7. the brazilian is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person driving the jet-ski##2
 8. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the malaysian##1
 9. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
10. the turkish is on the right of the person driving the van##1
11. the malaysian is on the right of the brazilian##1
12. the person driving the taxi is the nigerian##1
13. the spanish is on the left of the brazilian##1
14. the spanish is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
15. the nigerian is on the far right##1
16. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3       |    4     |   5    |     6     |    7     |
| Nationality   | italian | american      | spanish     | brazilian  | malaysian | turkish | nigerian |
| Sport         | rowing  | golf | tennis | swimming | rugby | baseball   | cycling  |
| Transport     | motorbike   | snowmobile     | jet-ski        | subway  | van   | airplane       | taxi      |

